<section class="cta-final" id="contacto-cta">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <h2>¿Listo para que tu negocio<br>trabaje las 24 horas?</h2>
    <p>El primer paso es un diagnóstico gratuito de tu negocio. Te mostramos exactamente dónde estás perdiendo clientes y cómo solucionarlo con marketing digital, automatización e inteligencia artificial.</p>
    <div class="cta-btns">
      <a href="#contacto" class="btn-primary">Quiero mi diagnóstico gratis</a>
      <a href="#servicios" class="btn-secondary">Ver nuestros servicios</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ── Sección ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .cta-final {
    background: #161616;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 7rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Glow radial centrado */
  .cta-final::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(113, 72, 252, 0.22) 0%, transparent 65%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ── Contenido ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .cta-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-final h2 {
    font-family: 'Avant Garde', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }

  .cta-final p {
    font-family: 'Graphie', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.25rem;
  }

  /* ── Botones ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .cta-btns {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: 'Graphie', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #fff;
    color: #161616;
    border: 2px solid #fff;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: 'Graphie', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: transparent;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    color: #fff;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  /* ── Responsive ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta-final {
      padding: 5rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .cta-btns {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
